title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1987-10-02

taper: Recorded by Joani Walker -- Tapes supplied by Paul Scotton
description:
Set I
Cold Rain & Snow

Stagger Lee
Me & My Uncle >
Mexicali Blues

Set II

Encore:
Black Muddy River

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar

Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
